### Obtener todas las compras
GET http://localhost:3000/api/compras


### Obtener compra por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/compras/1


### Crear una nueva compra
POST http://localhost:3000/api/compras
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "compradorId": 1,
  "cartasIds": [101, 102],
  "items": [
    { "cartaId": 101, "quantity": 2, "price": 9.99, "title": "Charizard" },
    { "cartaId": 102, "quantity": 1, "price": 4.5, "title": "Pikachu" }
  ],
  "total": 24.48,
  "estado": "pendiente",
  "nombre": "Juan Perez",
  "email": "juan@example.com",
  "telefono": "3412345678",
  "direccion": "Calle Falsa 123",
  "ciudad": "Rosario",
  "provincia": "Santa Fe",
  "codigoPostal": "2000",
  "metodoPago": "tarjeta"
}


### Actualizar compra (PUT - reemplaza recursos)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/compras/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "compradorId": 1,
  "cartasIds": [101],
  "items": [
    { "cartaId": 101, "quantity": 3, "price": 9.99, "title": "Charizard" }
  ],
  "total": 29.97,
  "estado": "pagado",
  "nombre": "Juan Perez",
  "email": "juan@example.com",
  "telefono": "3412345678",
  "direccion": "Calle Falsa 123",
  "ciudad": "Rosario",
  "provincia": "Santa Fe",
  "codigoPostal": "2000",
  "metodoPago": "tarjeta"
}


### Modificar compra (PATCH - parcial)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/compras/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "estado": "enviado"
}


### Eliminar compra
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/compras/1
